--- 
<section class="py-24 relative">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-5 lg:px-5 mx-auto">
        <div class="w-full justify-start items-center gap-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1">
            <div class="w-full flex-col justify-start lg:items-start items-center gap-10 inline-flex">
                <div class="w-full flex-col justify-start lg:items-start items-center flex">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl sm:tracking-tight mb-1">About me</h2>
                    <p class=>
                        When I'm not thinking about how systems connect, I'm at home in sunny Portugal in the my wonderfull chaotic place. My
                        partner Rita and I share our space with one dog named Lua and three cats: Mel, Croquete, and Amora.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        At 31, I find myself in an interesting phase of deliberately broadening my horizons. While I still love the intellectual
                        challenge of software engineering, I'm discovering that the best solutions often come when you step away from the screen
                        and let your mind wander through other pursuits.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>I've been trying to read more than just technical books.</li>
                        <li>I'm learning to play guitar and (maybe!) how to sing.</li>
                        <li>I love cooking and have a particular weakness for baking sourdough.</li>
                        <li>I also love to play games. I have all the consoles!</li>
                        <ul></div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative">
                        <!-- Still Image -->
                        <img
                        id="stillImage"
                            src="img/me.jpg"
                            alt="Still image"
                            class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-2xl transition-opacity duration-500"/>
                        <!-- Video (hidden initially) -->
                        <video
                            id="liveVideo"
                            class="absolute inset-0 w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-2xl opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"
                            muted
                            preload="metadata">
                            <source src="/video/me_live.mp4">
                                Your browser does not support the video tag.
                            </video>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <script>
                        const stillImage = document.getElementById('stillImage');
                        const liveVideo = document.getElementById('liveVideo');
                        let hasPlayedOnce = false;
                        // Auto play after 5 seconds
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            if (! hasPlayedOnce) {
                                playLivePhoto();
                            }
                        }, 5000);
                        function playLivePhoto() {
                            hasPlayedOnce = true;
                            // Fade to video
                            stillImage.style.opacity = '0';
                            liveVideo.style.opacity = '1';
                            liveVideo.currentTime = 0;
                            liveVideo.play();
                            // Return to still image when video ends
                            liveVideo.addEventListener('ended', () => {
                                setTimeout(() => {
                                    liveVideo.style.opacity = '0';
                                    stillImage.style.opacity = '1';
                                });
                            });
                        }
                        // Preload video for smoother playback
                        liveVideo.addEventListener('loadedmetadata', () => {
                            liveVideo.currentTime = 0;
                        });
                    </script>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="carousel" class="carousel carousel-center bg-neutral rounded-box w-full space-x-4 ">
                <div class="carousel-item max-w-xl">
                    <img src="img/amora.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Amora"/>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item max-w-xl">
                    <img src="img/mel.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Mel"/>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item max-w-xl">
                    <img src="img/croquete.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Croquete"/>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item max-w-xl">
                    <img src="img/amora_mel.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Amora and Mel"/>
                </div>
            </section>
        </section>